Package io.spine.server.command.model

This package provides model classes and interfaces for io.spine.server.command.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CommandHandlingClass<H extends CommandAcceptingMethod>
    A common interface for classes that handle commands.
    CommandingMethod<M extends io.spine.type.MessageClass,C extends com.google.protobuf.Message,R extends MethodResult>
    Base interface for methods that generate one or more command messages in response to an incoming message.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCommandHandlingClass<C,H extends CommandAcceptingMethod<?,?>>
    Abstract base for classes providing message handling information of classes that handle commands.
    CommandAcceptingMethod<T,R extends MethodResult>
    An abstract base for methods that accept a command message and optionally its context.
    CommanderClass<C extends Commander>
    Provides information on message handling for a class of Commanders.
    CommandHandlerClass<C extends CommandHandler>
    Provides message handling information on a command handler class.
    CommandHandlerMethod
    The wrapper for a command handler method.
    CommandHandlerMethod.Result
    The result of a command handler method execution.
    CommandingMethod.AbstractPredicate<C extends com.google.protobuf.Message>
    Abstract base for commanding method predicates.
    CommandSubstituteMethod
    A method that produces one or more command messages in response to an incoming command.
    CommandSubstituteMethod.Result
    A command substitution method returns a one or more command messages.
